| [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arithmetic_mean Average] value of the arguments, same as sum(a; b; c; ...) / count(a; b; c; ...)
| all
|-
| {{incode|count(a; b; c; ...)}}
| [https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Counting Count] of the arguments, typically used for cell ranges
